PrecisAcceptance of a DESIGNATION wherein the OSOYOOS INDIAN BAND surrenders, for a term of 99 years, approximately 95 hectares of land (Lot 196) on Osoyoos Indian Reserve No. 1 in British Columbia, for the purpose of leasing them to third parties for the various kinds of ventures specified therein.
